    "• We introduce and evaluate metadata appending as a method for accelerating pretraining, and highlight metadata types that are particularly suitable as auxiliary signals in this setup (Section 4.2).",
    "• We show that learnable meta tokens can partially recover the speedup with metadata, where attention patterns to these tokens encode quality-aware information.",
    "(Section 4.4).",
    "• We conduct layer-wise probing of latent representations for topic, quality, and authorship, providing mechanistic insight into how these factors are better encoded in the latent space (Section 4.5).",
